org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.batch.spi

Class OperationsQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.batch.spi.OperationsQueue

  • public class OperationsQueue
extends Object
    A queue for Operation.

    It keeps track of the element that are going to be affected by an InsertOrUpdateTupleOperation. The queue can be closed, in that case it will throw an exception when trying to add or poll an operation.

    Author:
    Guillaume Scheibel <guillaume.scheibel@gmail.com>, Davide D'Alto <davide@hibernate.org>
